Package: async
Version: 0.4.0-9000
Depends:
  R (>= 3.1.2),
  listenv,
  future
Imports:
  BatchJobs (>= 1.6.0),
  globals,
  parallel,
  R.methodsS3,
  R.oo,
  R.utils
Title: Asynchronous Evaluation
Authors@R: c(person("Henrik", "Bengtsson", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                                          email = "henrikb@braju.com"))
Description: Easy asynchronous evaluation of R expressions where global variables are taken of automatically.  This package provides an 'async future' that can be used with the Future API of the 'future' package.
License: Private for now [will become LGPL (>= 2.1) when published]
LazyLoad: TRUE
URL: https://github.com/HenrikBengtsson/async
BugReports: https://github.com/HenrikBengtsson/async/issues
